0:18:51.740,0:18:52.880
Handisi kukunzwa.

0:18:52.880,0:19:02.340
Mumwe munhu Andibata, nokuti ndinonzwa kuti simba rabuda kwandiri.

0:19:02.340,0:19:06.140
Mumwe munhu Andibata,

0:19:06.140,0:19:07.280
Ani?

0:19:07.280,0:19:12.300
Ini.

0:19:12.300,0:19:13.540
Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari.

0:19:13.540,0:19:15.020
[Ameni.]

0:19:15.020,0:19:22.180
Yave nguva zvino yekuti urambe uchifungisisa mumwoyo mako.

0:19:22.180,0:19:24.900
Uri kufungisisa chii?

0:19:24.900,0:19:32.720
Ishe Jesu, ndiitei nzira yenyu - nzira yeruregerero.

0:19:32.720,0:19:38.780
Ndiitei mukana wenyu - mukana wekuregerera.

0:19:38.780,0:19:47.340
Ndiitei nzira yenyu - nzira yekuchena, o, Ishe Jesu.

0:19:47.340,0:19:50.080
Zviri nyore - izvozvo ndizvo zvinhu zvaunofanira kufungisisa nezvazvo.

0:19:50.080,0:19:54.020
Iwe unogona kugara pasi apo kufungisisa kwako kurikuenderera mberi.

0:19:54.020,0:19:57.000
Ndiyo nzira chete iyo unogona kudzikinurwa nayo.

0:19:57.000,0:20:01.200
Mhando yemunyengetero waunopa mazuva ano haigoni kukubatsira.

0:20:01.200,0:20:08.020
Iwe wakajaira kuti ne zita ra Jesu, Ishe Jesu ...

0:20:08.020,0:20:09.820
Zvinhu zvose izvozvo hazvigoni kukubatsira.

0:20:09.820,0:20:13.000
Dai zvinhu izvozvo zvichikubatsira, zvingadai zvakubatsira.

0:20:13.000,0:20:18.680
Udza waugere naye, "Dai munyengetero uyu waigona kukubatsira, ungadai wakakubatsira".

0:20:18.680,0:20:23.880
Iwe unoziva, wakanga uri mazviri  Jesu, Jesu Jesu...

0:20:23.880,0:20:24.920
Izvi hazvigoni kukubatsira.

0:20:24.920,0:20:28.500
Iwe unoda kufungisisa kuti ubude kubva mune zvakaipa izvi.

0:20:28.500,0:20:34.700
Udza waugere naye, "Iwe unoda kufungisisa kuti ubude kubva muzvakaipa izvi."

0:20:34.700,0:20:39.820
Kana Jesu ari Mweya iwe unofanira kutanga kuita ruzha urwu.

0:20:39.820,0:20:47.520
Asi iwe unodanidzira "Jesu" kwete muchechi asi kumba, sekunge Iye muvakidzani wako.

0:20:47.520,0:20:51.360
Zvinhu izvozvo unyengeri.

0:20:51.360,0:20:55.920
Vanhu vanosarudza kuva vechitendero, kubva kwatinobva tose.

0:20:55.920,0:21:01.160
Takanga tiri vanhu vechitendero, tisati tatendeukira kuchi Kristu.

0:21:01.160,0:21:04.940
Nhasi, vanhu vari kudzokera kunzira dzavo dzechitendero.

0:21:04.940,0:21:08.240
Pane unyengeri mazviri.

0:21:08.240,0:21:14.340
Hakuna kubatana, godo neshanje pakati pemakereke,

0:21:14.340,0:21:16.660
"Uyu ndiye dhimoni, uyu ndiye satani."

0:21:16.660,0:21:19.480
Ndiani zvino ari mwana wa Mwari?

0:21:19.480,0:21:23.620
Dhiyabhorosi na satani zvino ava kushanduka kuva mwana wa Mwari.

0:21:23.620,0:21:29.500
Pane hunyengeri hwakawanda, kusabatana ...

0:21:29.500,0:21:33.300
Kufungisisa kushanyirana na Mwari.

0:21:33.300,0:21:34.360
Udza waugere naye.

0:21:34.360,0:21:37.140
[Kufungisisa kushanyirana Mwari.]

0:21:37.140,0:21:42.620
Ichi ndicho chikonzero Bhaibheri rinoti, "Nyengetera usingagumi".

0:21:42.620,0:21:47.640
Munyengetero chinhu chemwoyo, kwete chinhu chemuviri.

0:21:47.640,0:21:55.420
Nhasi munyengetero unova chinhu chemuviri, asi chiri chinhu chemwoyo.

0:21:55.420,0:21:58.380
Ndinogona kunge ndichitaura newe ikozvino, asi ndiri kunamata panguva imwe chete.

0:21:58.380,0:21:59.460
Izvi zvinogoneka sei?

0:21:59.460,0:22:03.000
Ndiri kutaura newe uye panguva imwechete ini ndiri kunyengetera.

0:22:03.000,0:22:08.720
Zvinokwanisika nokuti munyengetero chinhu chemumwoyo.

0:22:08.720,0:22:17.040
Mwoyo yedu inogona kuita zvinhu gumi panguva imwechete - inzvimbo ya Mwari, iyo inzvimbo yekufungisisa,

0:22:17.040,0:22:20.040
iyoyo inzvimbo yeruwadzano.

0:22:20.040,0:22:23.560
inzvimbo yeutsvene,

0:22:23.560,0:22:26.220
iyoyo inzvimbo yekutungamirira,

0:22:26.220,0:22:30.960
iyoyo inzvimbo yeushumiri - iwo mwoyo.

0:22:30.960,0:22:38.520
Kana iwe uchiti iwe unofanira kudanidzira paunonyengetera, unonyengetera sei paunorara?

0:22:38.520,0:22:41.760
Unofanirwa kunamata paunorara.

0:22:41.760,0:22:47.060
Zvinoita ropa kumhanya mumuviri mako ndiyo nzira iyo munyengetero unofanirawo kumhanya.

0:22:47.060,0:22:48.640
Icho chikamu chinokosha.

0:22:48.640,0:22:51.680
Ichocho chinhu chekutenda.

0:22:51.680,0:22:54.040
Izvi ndizvo zvinhu zvaufanira kuti ukunde.

0:22:54.040,0:22:56.820
Iwe unofanira kugona izvi kuti uponeswe.

0:22:56.820,0:23:01.480
Kana zvisina kudaro, satani anoziva apo iwe usiri kunyengetera uye iye achakubata ipapo.

0:23:01.480,0:23:04.400
Haazombokubata paunenge uchinamata;

0:23:04.400,0:23:07.700
iye anoziva kuti haunamati nguva dzose, iwe une nguva yekunyengetera.

0:23:07.700,0:23:11.020
Nguva iyo iwe usiri kunyengetera, anowanzokubata iwe.

0:23:11.020,0:23:14.680
Paunotarisa matambudziko awakanga uinawo, dzaive nguva yawaive usinga nyengetere.

0:23:14.680,0:23:16.040
Iwe unoti, "Ndiri kunonyengetera."

0:23:16.040,0:23:19.800
Usati wasvika ipapo satani anokubata.

0:23:19.800,0:23:23.880
Satani anoziva zvinhu izvozvo uye iye anga achikubata iwe saizvozvo.

0:23:23.880,0:23:30.560
Ichi ndicho chikonzero 90% chekurwiswa nhasi chiri mukurota.

0:23:30.560,0:23:34.380
Nokuti anoziva kuti iwe hauna chinhu apo unorara.

0:23:34.380,0:23:38.800
Pavanokurwisa muchiroto, chinhu ichocho chichaonekwa muhupenyu chaihwo.

0:23:38.800,0:23:44.160
Kana mumwe akarwiswa nezuro usiku, chinhu ichocho chichatanga kuratidzira nhasi.

0:23:44.160,0:23:53.380
Kana kwaiva kupfurwa nepfuti, kunotanga kuratidzira nekuitika mune rimwe remazuva anotevera.

0:23:53.380,0:24:01.600
Zvinogona kunge zvaiva chekudya chawakapiwa muchiroto; apo iwe unomuka chinhu ichocho chinotanga kuratidzira.

0:24:01.600,0:24:05.960
Chimwe chinhu chakadaro ... zvechokwadi.

0:24:05.960,0:24:11.500
Vakasarudza kukurwisa iwe muchiroto nokuti vanoziva kuti iwe hauna simba rekufungisisa.

0:24:11.500,0:24:17.420
Paunofungisisa, iwe unofungisisa nguva dzose uye paunorara, kufungisisa kunoenderera

0:24:17.420,0:24:20.500
nokuti isimba ra Mwari; harisi simba rako.

0:24:20.500,0:24:24.120
Uyu munyengetero waunopa nhasi isimba rako, kwete simba ra Mwari.

0:24:24.120,0:24:26.800
Nokudaro, iwe haugoni kushanda muchiroto.

0:24:26.800,0:24:30.960
Paunofungisisa nekuzopedzisira wakarara, kufungisisa kuchaenderera

0:24:30.960,0:24:33.380
nokuti mwoyo wako ndiwo uri kuzviita.

0:24:33.380,0:24:36.380
Mwoyo wako hauzombomira kana wakarara.

0:24:36.380,0:24:42.500
Mwoyo wako unoshanda paunenge uvete uye mwoyo mumwe chete ndiyo unenge uchifungisisa.

0:24:42.500,0:24:50.000
Muviri wako unoguma pakarepo paunorara asi mwoyo unoramba uchienderera.

0:24:50.000,0:24:53.760
Kufungisisa ndekwe mumwoyo.

0:24:53.760,0:25:01.500
Iko kufungisisa kuchava chizaruro chinoratidzira kuburikidza nehupenyu hwako.

0:25:01.500,0:25:08.720
Apo pane rima, uye iwe unokumbira Mwari kuti akuite iwe nzira ye chiedza - kune kurwisa kunobva kurima

0:25:08.720,0:25:17.900
- iwe unongoona kuratidzwa kwahwo nokuti uri nzira yechiedza kuna Mwari.

0:25:17.900,0:25:20.880
Mwoyo unofanira kudzikinurwa kuti ufungisise.

0:25:20.880,0:25:22.260
Udza waugere naye.

0:25:22.260,0:25:24.240
[Mwoyo unofanirwa kununurwa kuti ufungisise.]

0:25:24.240,0:25:25.640
Kufungisisa.

0:25:25.640,0:25:33.080
Mwoyo kureva M W O Y O.

0:25:33.080,0:25:36.060
Mwoyo unoreva mweya wako.

0:25:36.060,0:25:37.040
Udza waugere naye.

0:25:37.040,0:25:38.360
[Mwoyo zvinoreva mweya wako.]

0:25:38.360,0:25:41.660
Pandinotaura mwoyo ndinoreva mweya wako.

0:25:41.660,0:25:44.740
Mweya womunhu zvinoreva mwoyo.

0:25:44.740,0:25:51.500
Mwoyo wako unoda kudzikinurwa kuti ufungisise nekuti zvinhu zvakawanda zviri kuitika mumwoyo mako.

0:25:51.500,0:25:59.640
Kugamuchira kuri nyore kwazvo - kuporeswa ne kununura zviri patafura yako kare;

0:25:59.640,0:26:03.680
uchazvichengetedza sei?

0:26:03.680,0:26:10.600
Iwe haugone kuchengetedza hupenyu hwako, vhudzi rako, dhirezi rako, sutu yako - haugone kuchengetedza.

0:26:10.600,0:26:12.920
Iwe haugoni kunyange kuchengetedza imba yako.

0:26:12.920,0:26:15.900
Iwe haugone kuchengeta vana vakapiwa kwauri na Mwari.

0:26:15.900,0:26:19.640
Iwe haugone kuchengeta murume wako kana mudzimai wako.

0:26:19.640,0:26:21.960
Iwe haugone kuchengeta motokari yaunayo.

0:26:21.960,0:26:24.320
Hatingataure ne pfuma yedenga.

0:26:24.320,0:26:31.440
Iwe haugone kuchengetedza bhizinesi rako, mubhadharo wako, mari yaunowana.

0:26:31.440,0:26:34.560
Kunyange shangu dzako - haugone kudzichengetedza.

0:26:34.560,0:26:39.620
Zviri nani kuti usagamuchira pane kugamuchira pasina chii?

0:26:39.620,0:26:41.180
[Ruchengetedzo.]

0:26:41.180,0:26:42.800
Zviri nani kusa ...

0:26:42.800,0:26:44.340
Kana ini ndichida kukupa izvi.

0:26:44.340,0:26:48.800
Kana iwe uchiziva kuti haugone kuzvichengetedza - usagamuchira.

0:26:48.800,0:26:52.200
Iwe unogona kungogamuchira chete kana iwe uchiziva kuti unogona kuzvichengetedza

0:26:52.200,0:26:58.420
nokuti iwe uchazonyanya kuzvida zvikuru mangwana, kwete nhasi.

0:26:58.420,0:27:03.940
Zvawave kuzogamuchira nhasi, uchazvida zvakanyanya mangwana.

0:27:03.940,0:27:07.140
Nhasi unoda kuporeswa - ichokwadi, unoda kuporeswa.

0:27:07.140,0:27:09.840
Asi iwe uchada kumwe kuri nani mangwana.

0:27:09.840,0:27:16.560
Kana iwe zvino ukurasikirwa nako panguva yaunenge uchikudisa zvikuru - basa racho nderei?

0:27:16.560,0:27:19.200
Ndokusaka tiri kutaura nezvekuchengetedza.

0:27:19.200,0:27:20.540
Hongu.

0:27:20.540,0:27:27.980
Kufungisisa mudziyo waunoshandisa kugamuchira kubva kuna Mwari.

0:27:27.980,0:27:37.160
Kufungisisa mudziyo waungashandise kugamuchira kubva kuna Baba veku Denga.

0:27:37.160,0:27:41.080
Tiri kufungisisa nezvei?

0:27:41.080,0:27:42.340
Shoko ra Mwari.

0:27:42.340,0:27:47.640
Kana mumwe munhu achikuudza kuti iwe unogona kufungisisa pasina mwoyo, izvozvo hazvisi kufungisisa;uri kufunga.

0:27:47.640,0:27:52.880
Kufunga kuri mu imba duku - kufungisisa ndekwe imba yepamusoro - mwoyo.

0:27:52.880,0:27:59.260
Kufunga kamuri yekutandarira, kufungisisa ikamuri yekurara.

0:27:59.260,0:28:04.500
Svondo yemusi we Svondo pa SCOAN

0:28:04.500,0:28:09.100
Dai ndakanga ndiri muenzi chete, hamungandibvumire kuti ndipinde mukamuri yenyu yekurara.

0:28:09.100,0:28:16.020
Iwe uchandigamuchira ini mukamuri yako yekutandarira, kundifadza ne kuita chero chaunoda wondirega ndichienda.

0:28:16.020,0:28:20.480
Asi ini ndinofanira kuva nhengo yemba ndisati ndapinda mukamuri yako yekurara.

0:28:20.480,0:28:26.080
Kufungisisa ibhedhuru, kufunga ikamuri yekutandarira.

0:28:26.080,0:28:34.140
Ichi ndicho chikonzero tichiti Shoko rinofanira kuve rakakosha kwauri - richirarama mauri, richikuraira, richikutonga.

0:28:34.140,0:28:36.640
Paunenge wadzikinurwa, mwoyo wako uchava wakasununguka.

0:28:36.640,0:28:37.600
[Ameni.]

0:28:37.600,0:28:42.320
Kufungisisa kunogona kushanda chete kana iwe uine mweya wakasununguka -mwoyo wakasununguka.

0:28:42.320,0:28:43.560
Mwoyo wakasununguka unofungisisa.

0:28:43.560,0:28:44.440
Udza waugere naye.

0:28:44.440,0:28:45.960
[Mwoyo wakasununguka unofungisisa.]

0:28:45.960,0:28:48.080
Mweya wakasununguka unofungisisa.

0:28:48.080,0:28:49.540
[Mweya wakasununguka unofungisisa.]

0:28:49.540,0:28:55.540
Iwe unofunga, "Ndichagadzirisa sei dambudziko rangu?" Ndine chikwereti. "Ndaneta nenyika ino.

0:28:55.540,0:28:58.120
Mhuri yangu yose - tiri varombo. "

0:28:58.120,0:29:03.640
Zvose izvi kufunga ...

0:29:03.640,0:29:07.200
Iwe unofanira kusiya zvose izvi kuna Mwari.

0:29:07.200,0:29:14.680
Paunenge wazvisiya kuna Mwari, Anokwanisa; iwe unogona kufungisisa nemwoyo wako.

0:29:14.680,0:29:17.820
Izvi ndizvo zvandinoreva ne zvido zvako.

0:29:17.820,0:29:23.100
Zvido-zvako mumwoyo wako hazvizombotendera mwoyo wako kuti ufungisise.

0:29:23.100,0:29:28.340
Isu tinofungisisa musimba ra Mwari kana mwoyo yedu yakasununguka.

0:29:28.340,0:29:31.580
Uye mwoyo wemunhu unogona kusununguka patinenge tadzikinurwa.

